reviewText: Fun video for the kids.  Lots of music, with kids playing in water and elsewhere.

I saw the words Little Tikes and just knew my grand baby would love it...the DVD had been so good. I was very disappointed. The animation didn't look as good on this DVD as it did on the original. It was like a cheap imitation. I hope they come out with another one as good as the first. I'll buy it then.
